Definition: action mechanism in a modern rifle or shotgun
Example: a back and forward motion of a sliding lever ejects the empty shell case and cocks the firearm and loads a new round
Synonyms: slide_action, action, rifle, p, shotgun, mechanism, in, a, modern, or, back, and, forward, motion, of, sliding, lever, ejects, the, empty, shell, case, cocks, firearm, loads, new, round
Category: noun.artifact
